border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style=
: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> in many ways</a> a lot like (more regula=
ted versions of) stablecoins, and <em>they</em> don=E2=80=99t just put all =
their money in bank accounts. In part because they want to earn a bit more =
yield, but also because=C2=A0<em>as a risk management decision=C2=A0</em>pu=
tting all your money in an account with one bank has some drawbacks.</p><p =
style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another set of problems has to do with the people=
