 money in a bank account.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have tal=
ked about this problem before with Tether, the biggest stablecoin, which go=
t in trouble for=C2=A0doing <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.=
