>Tether Holdings Ltd. released the most detailed version yet of the assets =
backing its widely used digital currency, seeking to address regulatory con=
cerns that it hasn=E2=80=99t previously disclosed enough about the currency=
=E2=80=99s underpinnings. ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Roughly half =
of Tether=E2=80=99s $62.8 billion in assets were held in commercial paper a=
