said that 24% of its assets were in Treasury bills=E2=80=94considered among=
 the safest to hold=E2=80=94up from about 2.2% detailed in May. The other r=
oughly quarter of the reserves are held in a mix of corporate bonds, cash a=
nd small deposits.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24713966.262444/aHR0c=
HM6Ly90ZXRoZXIudG8vd3AtY29udGVudC91cGxvYWRzLzIwMjEvMDgvdGV0aGVyX2Fzc3VyYW5j=
ZWNvbnNvbGlkYXRlZF9yZXNlcnZlc19yZXBvcnRfMjAyMS0wNi0zMC5wZGY/607f07ceef4b852=
